MORNING REPORT: COMING ATTRACTIONS 
ABC's daytime "Home" show will be at Thursday night's rehearsal for Comic 
Relief III, taping talks with hosts Billy Crystal, Whoopi Goldberg and Robin 
Williams to air on the program Friday (10 a.m.) to mark the opening of the 800 
telephone number for pledges to aid the homeless. Comic Relief itself comes 
along Saturday night at 9 on Home Box Office cable. ALEENE MacMINN 
